						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/the-fisa-echelon-panopticon.html" title="Permalink to The FISA/Echelon Panopticon" rel="bookmark">The <span class="caps">FISA</span>/Echelon Panopticon</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/the-fisa-echelon-panopticon.html" title="20:20" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-02-15T20:20:00+00:00" pubdate>February 15, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
