												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/acta" title="View all posts in ACTA" rel="category tag">ACTA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/big-brother" title="View all posts in Big Brother" rel="category tag">Big Brother</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/civil-liberties" title="View all posts in Civil Liberties" rel="category tag">Civil Liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/current-affairs" title="View all posts in Current Affairs" rel="category tag">Current Affairs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/democracy" title="View all posts in Democracy" rel="category tag">Democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/drugs-2" title="View all posts in Drugs" rel="category tag">Drugs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/economics" title="View all posts in Economics" rel="category tag">Economics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/extradition" title="View all posts in Extradition" rel="category tag">Extradition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/ip" title="View all posts in IP" rel="category tag">IP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/leap" title="View all posts in LEAP" rel="category tag">LEAP</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/mi5" title="View all posts in MI5" rel="category tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/nsa" title="View all posts in NSA" rel="category tag">NSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/politics" title="View all posts in Politics" rel="category tag">Politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/tv" title="View all posts in TV" rel="category tag">TV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title="View all posts in Whistleblowers" rel="category tag">Whistleblowers</a>			</span>
