									<span class="sep"> | </span>
							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/chris-tappin" rel="tag">Chris Tappin</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/extradition-2" rel="tag">extradition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/gareth-peirce" rel="tag">Gareth Peirce</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/gary-mckinnon" rel="tag">Gary McKinnon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/jawad-botmeh" rel="tag">Jawad Botmeh</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/julian-assange" rel="tag">Julian Assange</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/richard-odwyer" rel="tag">Richard O'Dwyer</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/samar-alami" rel="tag">Samar Alami</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
